OL,3,CForbes: Next UK government must cut
OL,4,CVAT to help businesses
OL,6,FScotland's Deputy First Minister has
OL,7,Fdemanded the UK's next prime minister
OL,8,Fcommits to cutting the rate of VAT.
OL,10,FKate Forbes said the move would act as
OL,11,Fa "win-win-win" for businesses in the
OL,12,Fhospitality and tourism sectors after
OL,13,Fthey were "battered" by Covid-19 and
OL,14,FBrexit.
OL,16,FThe SNP included the proposal in its
OL,17,Fmanifesto launched on Wednesday, and
OL,18,FMs Forbes will highlight the issue
OL,19,Fduring a General Election campaign
OL,20,Fvisit in Glasgow on Friday.
