OL,3,CForbes: Next UK government must cut
OL,4,CVAT to help businesses
OL,6,FShe said: "Cutting VAT for businesses
OL,7,Fwould be a 'win-win-win' for
OL,8,Fhospitality, tourism and the wider
OL,9,Feconomy.
OL,11,F"In the last few years, hospitality
OL,12,Fand tourism businesses have been
OL,13,Fbattered by the Covid pandemic, and
OL,14,Fthey are still being battered by
OL,15,FBrexit ` it's time that Westminster
OL,16,Fgave these businesses a break by
OL,17,Ffinally cutting VAT.
